            "title": "曦智科技暗盤中段較招股價高逾3.3倍 邁威生物暗盤微升約1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">明天將有兩隻新股掛牌，暗盤暫時表現差異頗大，其中曦智科技(01879)暗盤中段作價已較招股價高逾3.3倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：曦智科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260413_FI_source-web_Xizhi-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：曦智科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260413_FI_source-web_Xizhi-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：曦智科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至下午約5時04分，輝立交易平台顯示曦智科技暗盤價達793元，較最高招股價高3.33倍；富途顯示的暗盤價更達797.5元，高於招股價3.35倍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">同樣明天登場的新股邁威生物(02493)，暗盤價暫時卻相對失色。輝立交易平台顯示該股暗盤暫報27.98元，較招股價高1.23%；富途顯示的暗盤價28.02元，較招股價也只高1.38%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15927525-%e6%9b%a6%e6%99%ba%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e4%b8%ad%e6%ae%b5%e8%bc%83%e6%8b%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e9%ab%98%e9%80%be3-3%e5%80%8d-%e9%82%81%e5%a8%81%e7%94%9f%e7%89%a9%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260413_FI_source-web_Xizhi-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-27 17:09:55",
